Package: WeatherTripPlanner
Title: Weather Statistics for Trip Planning 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jasmin", "Hagemann", , "jasmin.hagemann@student.uva.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The package provides the user with weather statistics for a specific 
              location. It will rank different time periods according to the 
              user's temperature or precipitation preferences and display the
              weather parameters for the entered location at the selected times.
